-<h2>3. Layer Architecture (Data Flow)</h2>
-<div class="codehilite"><pre><span></span><code>External Sources                  API Layer (/backend)    Service Layer             Storage
-─────────────────    HTTP POST    ──────────────   calls  ──────────────  writes  ────────────
- WHONET / DHIS2  ──────────────► backbone.py ──────────► DataCleaner    ──────► PostgreSQL
-                                  (Router)            │  (cleaner.py)            (TimescaleDB)
-                                                      │
-                                                      │                             Kafka
-                                                      └──► (Event Stream) ──────► (Message Bus)
-                                                                                         │
-                                                                                         ▼
-                                                                                 ML/AI Services
-                                                                                   (/ml-ai)
-
-Auth Flow:  Client ──POST /token──► auth.py ──► security.py (JWT) ──► Bearer Token
-Protected:  Client ──Bearer───────► security.py (decode) ──► RoleChecker(required_role) ──► Route Handler
-</code></pre></div>
-
